title: WESTERN NIGHT AT THE BIJOU (Double Feature).

sources.title: WESTERN NIGHT AT THE BIJOU (Double Feature).
sources.description: This is a simulated double feature program in a second-run movie house: The oat-powered adventures begin with coming attractions and a cartoon. Then outlaw John Wayne tries to go straight in "Angel and the Bad Man," costarring adorable Gail Russell. In the second feature Tex Ritter and Dave O'Brien whup the bad guys in "Gangsters of the Frontier," a classic B-western shoot-em-up.
